<bibRefCitation author="Candolle, A. P. de" box="[234,477,410,437]" pageId="4" pageNumber="105" refId="ref2172" refString="Candolle, A. P. de (1825) Prodromus systematis naturalis regni vegetabilis, sive, Enumeratio contracta ordinum generum specierumque plantarum huc usque cognitarium, juxta methodi naturalis, normas digesta. Vol 2. Parisii: Sumptibus Sociorum Treuttel et Wu ¨ rtz. 644 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 286" type="book" year="1825">Candolle (1825: 352)</bibRefCitation>
